node.title: Man dies after crash involving truck and pedestrian in TÅ«rangi
node.description: The incident occurred at about 9:45pm on Sunday.
node.content: ["A man has died after a crash between a truck and a pedestrian near T\u016brangi on Sunday evening.\u00a0", "Police said the incident occurred at about 9:45pm on State Highway 1 just north of T\u016brangi.", "The road was closed in both directions at the time but is now reopened.", "The Serious Crash Unit will be in attendance and enquiries into the circumstances of the incident are ongoing.", "The death has been referred to the coroner."]
